title: China â€˜dictatesâ€™ terms to Bangladesh; Asks Dhaka to reject bloc politics, cold war mentality
description: Rattled by the QUAD, which includes U.S., Australia, India and Japan as its members, China has now given yet another advice to Bangladesh. After meeting Bangladesh Ambassador to China Mahbub Uz Zaman, Liu Jinsong, Director-General of the Department of Asian Affairs of the Chinese Foreign Ministry, said "China believes that countries in the region, including Bangladesh, will bear in mind the fundamental interests of their own countries and the region, uphold independence, reject the Cold War mentality and bloc politics." His comments come one year after China had publicly asked Bangladesh not to join the QUAD alliance. title: Pak buckles under IMF pressure: Imran calls for protest as Sharif hikes fuel prices again
description: The economic crisis in Pakistan is showing signs of worsening. In a bid to secure bailout money from International Monetary Fund, the Shehbaz Sharif government has yet again increased fuel prices by PKR 30 per litre. The 17% hike in prices is second since May 2022. Petrol in Pakistan is now priced at 209.86 PKR, diesel at 204.15 PKR, kerosene oil at 181.94 PKR and light diesel at 178.31 PKR. Only kerosene oil's price was hiked by less than 30 PKR. Pakistan Finance MInister Miftah Ismail said the government was holding talks with the IMF on a daily basis, adding "we cannot accept all their demands but there are certain points that we have to agree to." Watch this video for more details.|#pakistan #shehbazsharif #fuelpricehike #fuel #pak #petrolprice #petrol #diesel #dieselpricehike #kerosene #miftahismail #economy #economiccrisis

title: 100 days since Russia's invasion: Ukraine announces plans for a counter-offensive | Ukraine latest
description: As the Russian war enters its 100th day, Ukrainian President Zelenskyy has said he expects Western partners to send more advanced weapons to defend his country.|Ukraineâ€™s military has reported that it has managed to hold positions in the eastern city of Sievierodonetsk, and that fighting continues in the strategically important city. In a post on Facebook the Ukrainian general staff said that Russian forces were continuing their bombardment of Ukrainian positions in the city. The general staff also reported that there had been air strikes on the village of Myrna Dolyna and failed attempts to advance on two nearby settlements. Military leadership went on to say that there had also been a failed attempt to cut Sievierodonetsk from supply lines, but these were also unsuccessful. DW cannot independently verify the reports.|As the Russian invasion of Ukraine reaches 100 days, Moscow has not achieved any of its initial goals, according to a daily briefing by the British Defense Ministry. "Russian forces failed to achieve their initial objectives to seize Kyiv and Ukrainian centers of government," the UK ministry wrote, putting the failures down to Russian "false planning and poor tactical execution." Russian forces are having more success in Ukraine's eastern Donbas region, a part of the country that has witnessed a military standoff between Russian and Ukrainian forces since 2014. However, those gains, particularly in the Luhansk Oblast of the Donbas region, have come at a "significant resource cost" that has prevented Russian forces from generating momentum on other fronts. The war in Ukraine will continue for some time if the Kremlin is to reach its goals, the UK said.|In his nightly video address, Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy said brutal fighting continued in Ukraine's eastern Donbas region, particularly around the city of Sievierodonetsk. "It's the toughest there right now," he said. "The entire temporarily-occupied territory of our state is now a complete disaster zone, for which Russia bears full responsibility. "The longer the war goes on, the more vile, shameful and cynical things Russia is forever inscribing in its history," he added. Zelenskyy went on to thank the United States for agreeing to send advanced rocket systems. "These weapons really can save the lives of our people and defend our land," he said. According to Zelenskyy, Ukraine expects to receive modern combat systems from other countries and noted that Sweden announced Thursday it was sending a new package of military assistance. At the moment, Lando has 48 points, to Daniels 11 - so Lando has brought in 82% of McLarens points this season.|Then there is qualifying pace - on average, Lando is 6 tenths quicker - in the same car. (0.596)|So I looked into whatâ€™s going on, but to understand that - we need to understand Ricciardoâ€™s driving style. Because it will explain why he was so quick at Red Bull, but not at McLaren. |â€”|Quickly though, I need to mention that Danny has had some great results. With several podiums and even a win back in Monza. But what weâ€™re looking at is one of the drivers with the worst records compared to their teammate - who is obviously working with the same tools. |So really, it's the gap to Lando that is interesting here. |â€”|So what is Dannyâ€™s driving style like? Well, I have broken down a number of driving styles on this channel - and really, they are subtle points that allow the driver to get the car through the corner quickly. |For example, Hamilton is incredible on the brakes. He is able to get the car stopped well, without losing time on exit. Vettel takes a more veeâ€™d off line to rotate the car mid-corner, similar to Schumacher. |But all of these driving styles tie in closely with the car they are driving. For example, Alonso back in 2005 and 2005 was driving a Renault with a really strong rear end and using tyres that were rock hard. So he induced understeer on the way into the corner, which heated the tyres and gave him the grip to pivot the car mid-corner and fire it out on exit. |But he isnâ€™t using that style at Alpine for example, as it would chew up the tyres and he would be pretty slow. |â€”|But, having said that - Danny was at his peak at Red Bull between 2014 and 2018. title: Waktu Cuti Gubernur Jawa Barat Hanya hingga 4 Juni 2022, Ridwan Kamil Harus Berhenti Cari Eril
description: KOMPAS.TV - Sepekan lebih, Putra Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz yang tenggelam di Sungai Aare, Swis, belum ditemukan.||||Pihak keluarga menyebut telah mengikhlaskan dan menyatakan Eril meninggal dunia.||||Dalam keterangan pers yang disampaikan pagi tadi, Kakak Ridwan Kamil, Erwin Muniruzaman menyampaikan, pencarian Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz sudah dilakukan maksimal oleh otoritas setempat.||||Meski demikian, Adik Ridwan Kamil yang kini telah berada di Swiss menyebut, pencarian Eril akan terus dilakukan dengan menambah anjing pelacak yang memiliki keahlian khusus.||||Imbauan Salat Gaib dikemukakan Majelis Ulama Indonesia (MUI) Jawa Barat, karena Ridwan Kamil dan keluarga telah mengikhlaskan kepergian putra sulung mereka.||||Namun, meski pencarian terus dilakukan, upaya Ridwan Kamil menemani pencarian sang putra terpaksa terhenti.||||Ridwan Kamil harus kembali ke tanah air karena berakhirnya masa cuti Gubernur Jawa Barat pada 4 Juni 2022.||||RK akan diwakilkan sang adik yang memantau proses pencarian langsung di Swiss.||||Sebagai orang tua, Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia tentu tak henti harap menemukan keberadaan sang putra.||||Namun lewat sebuah pesan di media sosial, Atalia, sang ibunda||mengikhlaskan kepergian Eril.||||Bersama anak perempuannya Camillia Azzahra, mereka bertiga||bersimpuh pamit di tepian Sungai Aare.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/295423/waktu-cuti-gubernur-jawa-barat-hanya-hingga-4-juni-2022-ridwan-kamil-harus-berhenti-cari-eril

title: Area Pencarian Eril Akan Diperluas, Anjing Pelacak Diterjunkan
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - KBRI Bern kembali menyampaikan perkembangan terkini pencarian Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz, anak Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil yang dilaporkan hilang di sungai Aare sejak Kamis (26/5/2022) lalu.||||Dalam keterangan resmi KBRI Bern yang dipublikasikan melalui laman Kementerian Luar Negeri, pencarian Eril, sapaan akrab putra sulung Ridwan Kamil terus dilakukan dengan mengerahkan patroli darat, perahu dan drone.||||Baca Juga Petani di Ponorogo Buang Ribuan Liter Susu Segar Karena Wabah PMK di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295305/petani-di-ponorogo-buang-ribuan-liter-susu-segar-karena-wabah-pmk||||Pencarian yang dilakukan penyelam yang sudah dilakukan dalam beberapa hari terakhir kali ini tidak dapat dikerahkan lantaran pertimbangan derasnya arus sungai Aare kemarin.||||Adapun fokus pencarian akan dilakukan di Area Marzili hingga pintu air Engehalde, serta patroli di area Schwellenmaetelli hingga Wohlensee. Upaya pencarian juga akan kembali dilakukan esok dengan dukungan anjing pelacak.||||Hal tersebut juga ditegaskan oleh Elpi Nazmuzaman, selaku Paman Eril yang kini berada di Kota Bern, Swiss untuk menggantikan Ridwan Kamil melakukan pencarian Eril.||||Video Editor : Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/295317/area-pencarian-eril-akan-diperluas-anjing-pelacak-diterjunkan

description: Gulshan Kumar, T-Series & Reliance Entertainment present 'Sherdil: The Pilibhit Saga' Starring Pankaj Tripathi, Neeraj Kabi, and Sayani Gupta.|A hero to cheer for. A cause to fight for. A thought to die for.|#Sherdil - The Pilibhit Saga Trailer Out Now.|In Cinemas 24th June.|The film is inspired by true events. An insightful story about the adverse effects of urbanization, man-animal conflict and poverty leading to a bizarre practice in a village that resides on the edge of a forest.|In the Pilibhit Tiger Reserve in U.P. near the Indo-Nepal border, there reside some poor farmers on the edge of the forest. Their fortunes depend heavily on the monsoons failing which they are doomed to abject poverty. To counter that, they indulge in an inhuman and tragic practice of sending the elderly to the forest to be killed by tigers and then later collecting their bodies, planting them in the fields and then claiming lakhs of rupees as compensation from the Government. |The film revolves around Gangaram, who is a patriarch of a poor farmer family which is going through great hardships and poverty because of three consecutive failed monsoons. He decides he will not waste his death; he will adopt the infamous Tiger practice and will give up his life so that his family can have two square meals.  One fine day, he enters the forests and waits for his death. title: Keluarga Ridwan Kamil Yakini Eril Meninggal Dunia karena Tenggelam
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS TV - Pihak keluarga menyebut Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil telah ikhlas dan meyakini bahwa Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril meninggal dunia.||||Hal tersebut disampaikan oleh kakak kandung Ridwan Kamil di Bandung.||||"Kang Emil dan Teh Lia sudah meyampaikan bahwa mereka ikhlas dan meuakini bahwa Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz yang kita kenal sebagai Eril sudah wafat berpulang ke rahmatullah," ucap Erwin Muniruzaman.||||Baca Juga Cari Eril, Ridwan Kamil Susuri Sungai Aare Terakhir Kali Sebelum Pulang ke Indonesia di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295261/cari-eril-ridwan-kamil-susuri-sungai-aare-terakhir-kali-sebelum-pulang-ke-indonesia||||Pihak keluarga pun telah berkoordinasi dan konsultasi dengan MUI Jawa Barat terkait shalat ghaib untuk Eril.||||"Semalam, kami sudah langsung berkonsultasi dengan MUI Jabar menyampaikan konsultasi dan langkah selanjutnya," lanjutnya.||||Majelis Ulama Indonesia Jawa Barat (MUI Jabar) terbitkan surat seruan untuk laksanakan shalat ghaib atas musibah yang dialami Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril.||||Dalam surat yang diterbitkan Kamis (2/6), MUI Jawa Barat menyebut Ridwan Kamil dan keluarga telah mengikhlaskan Eril dan meyakini Eril meninggal karena tenggelam.|||| "Bapak Moch. Ridwan Kamil beserta istri sudah mengikhlaskan sepenuhnya dan meyakini bahwa ananda tercinta Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz sudah meninggal dunia karena tenggelam" tertulis di surat tersebut.||||Untuk itu, MUI Jawa Barat mengajak masyarakat melakukan shalat ghaib. Hal tersebut dilakukan untuk mengganti shalat jenazah.||||"Dengan memperhatikan syara, jenazah harus dishalatkan. Karena jenazah tidak/belum ditemukan maka shalat jenazah dilakukan dengan cara shalat ghaib" tertulis di sana.||||Eril dinyatakan meninggal dunia karena tenggelam, setelah hilang di sungai Aare dan dicari selama satu pekan penuh.||||Video Editor: Firmansyah|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/295275/keluarga-ridwan-kamil-yakini-eril-meninggal-dunia-karena-tenggelam

title: Mohan Bhagwat opposes Hindu groups bid to reclaim mosques; Wants 'amicable solution' for Gyanvapi

Mohan Bhagwat called for an amicable resolution to the Gyanvapi Mosque-Kashi Vishwanath temple dispute. Bhagwat suggested that both sides should sit across the table and find a solution. title: Momen Haru Ridwan Kamil Susuri Sungai hingga Azan Lepas Eril di Tepi Aare
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV - Ridwan Kamil kumandangkan azan di tepi sungai Aare, sebelum pulang ke Indonesia di tengah pencarian sang anak, Eril.||||Video tersebut viral di media sosial, termasuk video saat Ridwan Kamil susuri tepi sungai Aare.||||Dalam sebuah video, nampak Ridwan Kamil dengan sebuah tongkat susuri tepi sungai untuk mencari Eril.||||Baca Juga Keluarga Ridwan Kamil Yakini Eril Meninggal Dunia karena Tenggelam di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295275/keluarga-ridwan-kamil-yakini-eril-meninggal-dunia-karena-tenggelam||||Hal tersebut dilakukan Ridwan Kamil sebelum akhirnya ia dan keluarga pulang ke Indonesia.||||Sementara itu, Pihak keluarga menyebut Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil telah ikhlas dan meyakini bahwa Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril meninggal dunia.||||Hal tersebut disampaikan oleh kakak kandung Ridwan Kamil di Bandung.||||"Kang Emil dan Teh Lia sudah meyampaikan bahwa mereka ikhlas dan meuakini bahwa Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz yang kita kenal sebagai Eril sudah wafat berpulang ke rahmatullah," ucap Erwin Muniruzaman.||||Pihak keluarga pun telah berkoordinasi dan konsultasi dengan MUI Jawa Barat terkait shalat ghaib untuk Eril.||||Baca Juga Paman Ungkap Kebaikan Eril Saat-saat Terakhir di Sungai Aare: Pastikan Keselamatan yang Lain di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295289/paman-ungkap-kebaikan-eril-saat-saat-terakhir-di-sungai-aare-pastikan-keselamatan-yang-lain||||"Semalam, kami sudah langsung berkonsultasi dengan MUI Jabar menyampaikan konsultasi dan langkah selanjutnya," lanjutnya.||||Majelis Ulama Indonesia Jawa Barat (MUI Jabar) terbitkan surat seruan untuk laksanakan shalat ghaib atas musibah yang dialami Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril.||||Dalam surat yang diterbitkan Kamis (2/6), MUI Jawa Barat menyebut Ridwan Kamil dan keluarga telah mengikhlaskan Eril dan meyakini Eril meninggal karena tenggelam.||||Video Editor: Adrianus||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/295344/momen-haru-ridwan-kamil-susuri-sungai-hingga-azan-lepas-eril-di-tepi-aare

title: Sherdil-The Pilibhit Saga Official Trailer | Pankaj, Neeraj, Sayani | Srijit | In Cinemas 24th June
description: A hero to cheer for. A cause to fight for. A thought to die for.|#Sherdil - The Pilibhit Saga Trailer Out Now.|In Cinemas 24th June.|The film is inspired by true events. An insightful story about the adverse effects of urbanization, man-animal conflict and poverty leading to a bizarre practice in a village that resides on the edge of a forest. |In the Pilibhit Tiger Reserve in U.P. near the Indo-Nepal border, there reside some poor farmers on the edge of the forest. Their fortunes depend heavily on the monsoons failing which they are doomed to abject poverty. To counter that, they indulge in an inhuman and tragic practice of sending the elderly to the forest to be killed by tigers and then later collecting their bodies, planting them in the fields and then claiming lakhs of rupees as compensation from the Government.Â |The film revolves around Gangaram, who is a patriarch of a poor farmer family which is going through great hardships and poverty because of three consecutive failed monsoons. He decides he will not waste his death; he will adopt the infamous Tiger practice and will give up his life so that his family can have two square meals. Â One fine day, he enters the forests and waits for his death. What follows next is a series of unprecedented and interesting events.|It takes great courage to sacrifice oneâ€™s life to save the family and the film revolves around this heroism with a focus on the man & nature conflict.|â€˜Sherdil: The Pilibhit Sagaâ€™ |Presented by Gulshan Kumar, T-Series Film and Reliance Entertainment |Produced by Bhushan Kumar and Reliance Entertainment |Production by Match Cut Productions Private Limited |Written and Directed by Srijit Mukherji |Cast: Pankaj Tripathi, Neeraj Kabi, and Sayani Gupta.|For more information, log on:|https://www.relianceentertainment.com |Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RelianceEnt/  |Twitter: https://twitter.com/RelianceEnt |Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/reliance.entertainment/

title: Megadrought causes perilously low water levels at Lake Mead
description: The megadrought currently choking the western United States is the worst drought in the region in more than 1,000 years. It's having an enormous impact across many states and on several major reservoirs including Lake Mead, a water source for millions of people in the West. title: Man Shoots His Surgeon And Three People In Tulsa, Oklahoma Hospital
description: Four people were killed in a mass shooting in a St. Francis Hospital orthopedics office. Police say the gunman was 45-year-old Michael Louis who recently had back surgery in late May. title: Prince Louis STEALS THE SHOW at Trooping the Colour
description: Prince William and Kate Middleton's youngest son, Prince Louis, shows off his personality at Trooping the Colour, during Queen Elizabeth's Platinum Jubilee celebration. The family, including Louis' older brother and sister, Prince George and Princess Charlotte, all stand alongside Queen Elizabeth II in honor of her 70 years on the throne. The festivities began Thursday and continue with many star-studded gatherings through Sunday. These events will mark the first time the monarch is meeting Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's daughter, Lilibet.

title: Cameron Smith shoots 5-under 67 | Round 1 | The Memorial Tournament | 2022
description: In the opening round of the 2022 Memorial Tournament presented by Workday, Cameron Smith carded a 5-under 67 to join five other players in a tie for the lead heading into Friday.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||This week, the PGA TOUR heads to Muirfield Village Golf Club for the Memorial Tournament presented by Workday. Reigning FedExCup champion Patrick Cantlay returns to defend his title as seven of the top-10 players in the Official World Golf Ranking are all set to tee it up. Collin Morikawa, who lost to Patrick Cantlay in a playoff in 2021, will be looking for his first victory of the PGA TOUR season. After a strong start to the year, the American has finished outside the top 20 in his last three tournaments. While Jon Rahm returns as a past winner, world No. 3 Cam Smith will be hoping to claim his third title of the year after winning the Sentry Tournament of Champions and THE PLAYERS Championship. Viktor Hovland, Rory McIlroy and Jordan Spieth are the other top-10 players in the field in Dublin, Ohio. title: Cameron Smith headlines six-way tie after 18 holes at the Memorial | 2022
description: In the opening round of the 2022 Memorial Tournament presented by Workday, six players carded 5-under 67â€™s to tie for lead heading into Friday.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||This week, the PGA TOUR heads to Muirfield Village Golf Club for the Memorial Tournament presented by Workday. Reigning FedExCup champion Patrick Cantlay returns to defend his title as seven of the top-10 players in the Official World Golf Ranking are all set to tee it up. Collin Morikawa, who lost to Patrick Cantlay in a playoff in 2021, will be looking for his first victory of the PGA TOUR season. After a strong start to the year, the American has finished outside the top 20 in his last three tournaments. While Jon Rahm returns as a past winner, world No. 3 Cam Smith will be hoping to claim his third title of the year after winning the Sentry Tournament of Champions and THE PLAYERS Championship. Viktor Hovland, Rory McIlroy and Jordan Spieth are the other top-10 players in the field in Dublin, Ohio. title: Cari Eril, Ridwan Kamil Susuri Sungai Aare Terakhir Kali Sebelum Pulang ke Indonesia
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Ridwan Kamil susuri sungai Aare untuk terakhir kalinya sebelum pulang ke Indonesia bersama istri dan anaknya.||||Update pencarian Eril hingga Jumat (3/6) pagi masih terus dilanjutkan. Adik kandung Ridwan Kamil, Elpi Nazmuzaman gantikan peran Ridwan Kamil di Swiss.||||Elpi dan sejumlah keluarga akan menetap di Swiss mendampingi pihak berwenang untuk lanjutkan proses pencarian Eril.||||Baca Juga Ridwan Kamil Pulang ke Indonesia, Pencarian Eril Dilanjutkan sang Paman di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295258/ridwan-kamil-pulang-ke-indonesia-pencarian-eril-dilanjutkan-sang-paman||||Sementara itu KBRI Bern menyebut proses pencarian Eril dilanjutkan dengan tambahan metode anjing pelacak.||||Pencarian difokuskan di beberapa titik, termasuk pintu air di sungai Aare.||||Ridwan Kamil kembali ke Indonesia untuk melanjutkan tugasnya sebagai Gubernur Jawa Barat.||||Sebelumnya, Atalia sang istri telah mengunggah pesan berpamitan pada Eril melalui Instagramnya.||||"Ril mamah pulang dulu ke Indonesia, ya..||Mamah titipkan kamu dalam penjagaan dan perlindungan terbaik dari pemilikmu yang sebenarnya, Allah swt, dimana pun kamu berada Insya Allah kamu tidak akan kedinginan, kelaparan atau kekurangan apapun. Bahkan kamu akan mendapatkan limpahan kasih sayang, karunia dan kebahagiaan yang tak pernah putus," tulis Atalia di Instagram.||||Video Editor: Adrianus||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/295261/cari-eril-ridwan-kamil-susuri-sungai-aare-terakhir-kali-sebelum-pulang-ke-indonesia

title: Formula E Akan Dimulai, Ini Jawaban Anies DItanya Soal Pawang
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan menegaskan, Pemerintah Provinsi (Pemprov) DKI Jakarta tidak akan menggunakan pawang hujan saat pagelaran Jakarta E-Prix 2022 atau Formula E pada Sabtu (4/6/2022).||||Menurut dia, Pemprov DKI Jakarta sudah bekerja sama dengan Badan Meteorologi, Klimatologi dan Geofisika (BMKG) untuk membantu memonitor perkembangan cuaca.||||"Formula E enggak ada pawang-pawangan. Kita bekerja sama dengan BMKG untuk memonitor perkembangan cuaca. Bila terang kita syukuri, bila hujan kita syukuri," kata Anies dalam acara ngobrol santai dengan Co-Founder/Chief Championship Officer Operation Formula E, Alberto Longo di Balai Kota DKI Jakarta, Kamis (2/6/2022).||||Anies juga menegaskan, para pebalap Formula E sudah terbiasa menghadapi baik cuaca panas atau hujan. Oleh karena itu, ia menegaskan bahwa nantinya tidak akan ada pawang hujan dalam pelaksanaan Formula E.||||"Kami dari Pemprov DKI Jakarta selalu menggunakan ilmu pengetahuan dan data dalam bekerja," ujar dia. Sebelumnya, Formula E Operations (FEO) menyiapkan skenario dalam menghadapi cuaca buruk saat acara balapan Formula E di Ancol, Jakarta Utara, pada 4 Juni 2022.||||Principle HSE Consultant FEO, Richard Bates mengatakan, ada beberapa skenario yang disiapkan jika hujan deras atau ekstrem melanda kawasan sirkuit Ancol.||||Video Editor : Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/295252/formula-e-akan-dimulai-ini-jawaban-anies-ditanya-soal-pawang

title: Young Thug bond hearing livestream
description: UPDATE: The first case of the court session this morning is not Young Thug's. We will update this space when his hearing comes up.|UPDATE 2: The judge just addressed Young Thug by his legal name, Jeffrey Williams, and told him his hearing would still "be a minute."|UPDATE 3 (9:40 A.M.): The current hearing is for Yak Gotti, legal name Deamonte Kendrick, also involved in the RICO case.|UPDATE 4 (10:05 a.m.): Another case is now up, Young Thug's has still not yet been brought before the court.|UPDATE 5 (10:22 a.m.): The current proceeding is for Walter Murphy, who is also involved in the RICO case.|UPDATE 6: (10:30 a.m.): Another case is now proceeding that is unrelated to the RICO case.|UPDATE 7: (10:50 a.m.): Young Thug's hearing has still not come up. The currently called case is not related to the RICO case.|UPDATE 8: (11:20 a.m.): The court just wrapped up a guilty plea proceeding in an unrelated case, and is taking a 10-minute recess. Young Thug's case has not come up.|UPDATE 9: (11:50 a.m.): The court has returned from recess. The judge has read off the next case for Shannon Stillwell, who is part of the RICO indictment. He has also now read off the case for Young Thug, legal name Jeffrey Williams, which appears as if it will happen after Stillwell's proceeding.|UPDATE 10: (11:59 a.m.): The hold up appears to be that attorneys are currently discussing a conflict of interest issue.|UPDATE 11: (12:40 p.m.): They are still arguing the conflict of interest matter and whether Young Thug's attorney should be disqualified.|UPDATE 12: (1:01 p.m.): Apologies, we have lost our feed from the pool camera, which is being provided by another station on the designation of the court. We are working to get it back. The attorneys are still arguing about the conflict of interest matter.|UPDATE 13 (1:17 p.m.): We have the feed back for good. Apologies again about the interruption.|UPDATE 14 (1:37 p.m.): They seem to have completed making arguments about the conflict of interest/attorney disqualification matter, the judge says he is going to take a recess and consider things.|UPDATE 15: (2:12 p.m.):  The court is now taking up Young Thug's actual bond hearing.|-------|Atlanta rapper Young Thug is in court on Thursday morning for a bond hearing in his RICO gang case. title: Global National: June 2, 2022 | Thousands show appreciation, excitement for Queen's Platinum Jubilee
description: On this episode of Global National: Thousands of people gathered in London, England for the first day of festivities honouring Queen Elizabeth II's Platinum Jubilee, an event celebrating her historic 70-year reign. Crystal Goomansingh reports on the excitement among the sea of fans, what the 96-year-old monarch means to them, and how the party is extending way beyond Buckingham Palace. |As the Queen marks her historic milestone, questions keep growing over just how relevant the Royal Family remains in today's world. What will the monarchy look like in a post-Elizabethan world? Ross Lord explores the monarchy's challenges in maintaining its influence. |Also, from 1969 to 1986, the Queen rode only one horse for all her public events and parades: a black mare named Burmese. Dawna Friesen looks back at the monarch's special bond with her favourite steed, how it all began thanks to the RCMP, and how the pair overcame a terrifying moment in 1981. |Plus, international reaction is now pouring in following a Global News exclusive report, in which sources claimed Chinese fighter planes were flying dangerously close â€” aka "buzzing" â€” Canadian military aircraft. We have more on the reaction to this story from senior military leaders as well as from around the world. The YouTuber and actress also chatted about redefining success in her book, "Be a Triangle," being a judge on "Canada's Got Talent," and how it was for her to come out to her family as bisexual.

title: Quinta Brunson Witnessed a Sweet Marital Spat Between Dwyane Wade & Gabrielle Union
description: Actress Quinta Brunson recalled to guest host Dwyane Wade that she witnessed him and wife Gabrielle Union in a sweet marital spat at the Vanity Fair Oscars Party. Quinta also chatted about the inspirations behind her successful show, "Abbott Elementary."

title: Police shut down suspected illegal nightclub on Detroit's west side
description: Detroit police have shut down a bar they say has been operating as an illegal after-hours nightclub for months.  They raided the Wonderland Bar on Eight Mile Road just east of the Southfield Freeway Thursday (June 2) afternoon.

title: Taliban thanks India for helping Afghan people; Appeals to Modi govt to reopen Kabul Embassy
description: Taliban showers praise on India after the first meeting of two nations since its takeover in August 2021. The Taliban-run Afghanistan government thanked India for continuing its humanitarian and medical assistance. The Afghan Foreign Minister Amir Khan Muttaqi appealed India to resume its diplomatic and consular services. Muttaqi also requested India to resume its projects in the country. India's delegation headed by joint secretary JP Singh is currently in Kabul and is holding a series of meetings with Taliban leaders. title: How WANDA Started a War in DOCTOR STRANGE in the Multiverse of Madness
description: Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness showed Wanda disassembling the Illuminati--but there will be consequences for this action. She has brought down the wrath of The Fantastic 3, the Inhumans, X-Men, and all of the other heroes form this universe. It's only a matter of time before those heroes decide that the 616 universe is a threat that needs to be stopped. Here's how.|If you're new, Subscribe! â†’ http://bit.ly/subscribe-screencrush|Go here â†’ http://screencrush.com/|Like us â†’ https://www.facebook.com/ScreenCrush|Follow us â†’ https://twitter.com/screencrushnews|Get our newsletter â†’ http://screencrush.com/newsletter/|Written by Colton Ogburn (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_jYlGRqw02GGUNLkHmi69w)|Hosted by Ryan Arey (http://twitter.com/ryanarey)|Edited by Harriet Lengel-Enright, Randolf Nombrado, and Srinidhi Rao|In this universe Captain Carter is the first Avenger, Maria Rambeau is Captain Marvel, and maybe the Inhumans didnâ€™t suck. [clip, horrible clip from Inhumans]|I donâ€™t think weâ€™ve seen the last of Universe 838, in fact I think weâ€™re about to see Universe 838 declare war on the MCU AKA Universe 616. [clip, â€œI donâ€™t wanna fight you Flashâ€ but with 616 and 838 on their heads]|But before we get into that, let's take a moment to examine all we know about universe 838â€“because you know what they say: â€œknow your enemy.â€|The 838 seems almost utopic. As advanced as the MCUâ€™s technology is, the 838 seems to be even more so. [clip, Marty Mcfly reacting to the future.]|For example, the memory projectors on the street allow you to step into a circle and have a memory literally projected holographically in front of you. A technology very similar to Tony Starkâ€™s B.A.R.F. [clip]|And real quick while weâ€™re on that topic, Qunten Beck developed a lot of the technology for B.A.R.F. [clip, him being mad Tony named it B.A.R.F.]|Quentin Beck was the first character we heard refer to the MCU as universe 616. [clip]|Itâ€™s later revealed he was lying about being from another universe. So how he and the 838 Christine Palmer both came to call the MCU â€œ616â€ is something Iâ€™d be curious to know the answer to.|Anyway, back to the 838. Thereâ€™s almost something eerie about the perfection of this universe. I feel like their earth is very well protected from outside threats. Perhaps theyâ€™ve reached a point where they donâ€™t have daily catastrophes like in the MCU. [clips, kaiju size egyptian gods fighting in Moonknight, Wandaâ€™s hex, Doc Ock on the bridge, Endgame portal battle, one eyed octopus battle, etc.]|Catastropheâ€™s in the 838 are likely few and far between, but at what cost? Could earth 838 be ran by some type of underground secret organization pulling the strings and bending society to their will [eyeball in pyramid image begins to fade in over Ryan]|Doug: Oh because the Illuminati|Ryan: Yeah thatâ€™s what I was going for|But seriously, the 838 Illuminati may control more than we think. As utopic and well run as the 838 may be, thereâ€™s something scary about a bunch of unelected superheroes calling the shots. I mean thatâ€™s the entire premise of Captain America: Civil War.|What happens when the group of heroes running the show gets too cocky?|Doug: They let their guard down and get killed by a dream walking witch?|Ryan: Exactly.|In the comics the Illuminati was founded by Tony Stark. The group typically consists of Tony, Doctor Strange, Reed Richards, Professor X, Blackagar Boltagon AKA Black Bolt, Tâ€™Challa, and Namor the Submariner.|While Tony Stark isnâ€™t present in this film, his Ultron bots are. Assuming that in this universe Reed Richards or Hank Pym didnâ€™t create Ultron. I think itâ€™s also worth mentioning that there is a 7th seat that is empty in the Illuminatiâ€™s layer. So perhaps thatâ€™s Tonyâ€™s seat. [clip, Civil War scene where Tony tells Peter to â€œmove the legâ€ so he can sit.]|I think we can infer a lot about universe 838 from its unique Illuminati lineup. Each member seems to represent either a team or area of expertise. Reed Richards of the Fantastic 4 and quote â€œthe smartest man alive.â€ Black Bolt of the Inhumans. Professor Xavier represents mutantkind. Captain Carter is likely the leader of the 838 Avengers. Captain Marvel is the quote â€œdefender of the cosmos.â€ And following the death of the 838 Doctor Strange, Baron Carl Mordo is Sorcerer Supreme. [clip, Rick CARL!]|With members of this Illuminati representing some heavy hitting and very prominent teams in the Marvel universeâ€“their deaths will not be taken lightly.|Letâ€™s start with Professor X. The X-Men are going to be royally pissed that the Professor was killed.|Doug: But he already died twice.|#DrStrange #SecretWars #Marvel

title: Kyler Murray returns to Cardinals, Trey Lance faces ups & downs in SF, talks Aaron Donald | THE HERD
description: Albert Breer returns to The Herd to talk with Colin Cowherd about developments in the NFL offseason. The two discuss Kyler Murray, who returned to the Arizona Cardinals for the first time this offseason amid his contract dispute. Breer decides whether this is a good sign for Murray's future with the Cardinals. title: Konvoi Kelompok Khilafah Tuai Kontroversi, Pemimpin Khilafatul Muslimin Buka Suara!
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Konvoi sepeda motor beratribut Khilafatul Muslimin muncul di Cawang, Jakarta, Brebes, Jawa Tengah, dan Lampung sejak hari Minggu (30/05) hingga Kamis (02/06) ramai diperbincangkan.||||Sementara Forum Kerukunan Umat Beragama dari ormas islam dan Majelis Ulama Kabupaten Brebes, Jawa Tengah, sepakat menolak seluruh kegiatan Khilafatul Muslimin di Kabupaten Brebes .||||Munculnya konvoi Khilafatul Muslimin di Jakarta, Brebes, dan Lampung , Menteri Agama Yaqut Cholil Qoumas menegaskan, khilafah jelas dilarang di Indonesia.||||Baca Juga FKUB dan MUI Brebes Tegas Tolak Kegiatan Khilafah, Warga Diminta Jangan Mudah Terkecoh! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/294735/fkub-dan-mui-brebes-tegas-tolak-kegiatan-khilafah-warga-diminta-jangan-mudah-terkecoh||||Usai viral video konvoi motor beratribut khilafah, Abdul Qodir Hasan Baraja Kholifah atau Pemimpin Pusat Khilafutul Muslimin, tidak benar Khilafah menetang Negera Kesatuan Republik Indonesia (NKRI).||||Berdirinya Khilafatul Muslimin bertujuan menyatukan umat muslim maupun non-muslim untuk menjaga kesatuan NKRI.||||Kompas TV berdialog langsung dengan Islah Bahrawi, Direktur Eksekutif Jaringan Moderasi Beragama Indonesia dan Abdul Qodir Hasan Baraja Kholifah, Pemimpin Khilafatul Muslimin.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/295174/konvoi-kelompok-khilafah-tuai-kontroversi-pemimpin-khilafatul-muslimin-buka-suara

title: Pesan Atalia Istri Ridwan Kamil Pamit Pulang ke Indonesia: Mama Lepaskan Kamu..
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Istri Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil, Atalia Praratya unggah momen duduk saat bersama Ridwan Kamil dan anak kedua mereka di pinggir Sungai Aare, Swiss.||||Dalam pesan yang ditulis Atalia di akun instagramnya, Atalia pamit ke Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz yang hingga kini masih dinyatakan hilang di Sungai Aare.||||Berikut pesan lengkap Atalia yang diunggah pada Kamis (2/6/2022)||||Ril... mamah pulang dulu ke Indonesia, ya..||||Mamah titipkan kamu dalam penjagaan dan perlindungan terbaik dari pemilikmu yang sebenarnya, Allah swt, dimana pun kamu berada...||||Insya Allah kamu tidak akan kedinginan, kelaparan atau kekurangan apapun. Bahkan kamu akan mendapatkan limpahan kasih sayang, karunia dan kebahagiaan yang tak pernah putus.||||Disini, di sungai Aare yang luar biasa indah dan cantik ini, mamah lepaskan kamu, untuk kita bertemu lagi cepat atau lambat.||||Seperti yang pak walikota sampaikan,||||"The city of Bern will forever be deeply connected to us..."||||Doa terbaik mamah dalam setiap helaan nafas,||||Atalia||Aare river, juni 2022||||Video Editor: Arief Rahman||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/295158/pesan-atalia-istri-ridwan-kamil-pamit-pulang-ke-indonesia-mama-lepaskan-kamu

title: Queen's Platinum Jubilee: Trooping the Colour parade, military pageant to Buckingham Palace | FULL
description: Queen Elizabeth II's annual 2nd birthday parade kicked off four days of Platinum Jubilee festivities on June 2, when more than 1,200 officers and soldiers of the 1st Battalion and the Irish Guards put on a display of military pageantry through the streets of London, U.K. |They were joined by hundreds of army musicians and approximately 240 horses.|This livestream featured a variety of shots: Buckingham Palace forecourt, along the Mall, Horse Guards Parade (35:46) and the gun salute at Hyde Park (1:57:59) and a fly past.|2:04:36 Once the parade ended and the procession returned to the palace, the Royal Family made a balcony appearance, as they do every year.| |The Queen is the first British monarch to celebrate 70 years of service and will be honoured for the work sheâ€™s done for the people of the United Kingdom, the Commonwealth and the Realms.|For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/8880564/queen-elizabeth-platinum-jubilee-plans-events-schedule/|Subscribe to Global News Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/20fcXDc|Like Global News on Facebook HERE: http://bit.ly/255GMJQ|Follow Global News on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1Toz8mt|Follow Global News on Instagram HERE: https://bit.ly/2QZaZIB|#GlobalNews #QueenJubilee #PlatinumJubilee

title: Germany and US to send more heavy weapons to Ukraine as Russian forces advance in Donbas region
description: Barely two weeks after the last Ukrainian soldiers in the port city of Mariupol surrendered to the Russian army in hopes of a prisoner swap, Ukraine may lose yet another major center in the Donbasâ€” the city of Sievierodonetsk. Reportedly, there is fighting in the streets, and Russian soldiers are said to have advanced to the city center. Sievierodonetsk and neighboring Lyssychansk are the last major cities in the Luhansk area â€” the Donetsk and Luhansk regions are known collectively as the Donbas â€” still controlled by Kyiv. According to Ukraine's General Staff, Russia is intent on capturing Sievierodonetsk. Ukrainian troops defending the region risk being trapped, as they were in Mariupol.|Sievierodonetsk is also known for the fact that the first attempt to divide Ukraine was made there almost 20 years ago. On November 28, 2004, the so-called All-Ukrainian Congress of Deputies of All Levels convened in the city, attended mainlyby representatives of the pro-Russian Party of Regions. The party, formed in the Donbas, dominated the region. Against the backdrop of the pro-Western Orange Revolution protests in the capital Kyiv, it threatened to declare autonomy, with Kharkiv as its center and including eight eastern and southern Ukrainian regions as well as Crimea and Sevastopol.|Sievierodonetsk and neighboring Lyssychansk are of strategic importance because this part of the Donbas connects with other regions of Ukraine. The main focus is on the highway connecting Lysychansk with Bakhmut in Donetsk region. It is used to supply the Ukrainian military. It was also used to evacuate civilians before the route became too dangerous because of shelling. Capturing Sievierodonetsk and Lysychansk would allow the Russian army to reach the region's administrative border. From there, the Russian army could advance further west toward Kramatorsk, another administrative center in the Donetsk region. Kramatorsk is one of the last major industrial cities still fully controlled by Kyiv in the Donbas.|Ukraine's ambassador to Germany, Andriy Melnyk, has welcomed Chancellor Olaf Scholz's announcements on new arms deliveries. Itâ€™s a notable change of tone from Kyivâ€™s top diplomat in Berlin, who has been one of the German government's harshest critics, accusing it of being too hesitant in delivering weapons to Kyiv. Scholz on Wednesday announced in the Bundestag that the modern IRIS-T-SLM air defense system from the Diehl defense company would be supplied to Ukraine. The IRIS-T, developed in collaboration by Germany with other NATO partners, has the ability to target and shoot down other air-to-air and surface-to-air missiles. The chancellor also said Germany would supply Ukraine with radar systems to help locate enemy artillery.  "Finally, we can say from the bottom of our hearts to Chancellor Scholz: thank you!" said Melnyk. "Now we can really speak of a turning point for Ukraine. We hope for more modern weapons systems from Germany."   Melnyk said he hoped production could begin soon, followed by training and eventual deployment by October.  |Slovakia has said it will deliver eight self-propelled howitzers to Ukraine under a commercial contract signed with a state-controlled producer.  The ministry said the weapons were Zusana 2 howitzers, a modernized version of an older model that has an effective range of 40 kilometers (25 miles) to 50 kilometers. As well as its long range, the system is known for high accuracy and rate of fire.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Ukraine #Russia #Sievierodonetsk

title: Denmark holds referendum on dropping EU defence opt-out- BBC News
description: Danes have voted in a referendum on whether to scrap a 30-year opt-out and take part in EU defence and security policy.|Denmark is the only EU member that has a so-called defence reservation.|But like its Nordic neighbours, Sweden and Finland, it has been reassessing its security policy since Russia launched its war on Ukraine.|Opinion polls suggest Danes back closer European defence ties, and the result could affect their military future.|Equally, there has been plenty of confusion about what the vote means in a country that is already part of Nato's defensive alliance.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#Denmark #BBCNews

title: CUTE POLYMER CLAY CRAFTS || Mini Decor and DIY Jewelry
description: Hi, crafters! ||Are you looking for new ideas for using polymer clay? We will show you fresh step-by-step tutorials to inspire you to create some cool new polymer clay jewelry and decor items. You can take a piece of yellow polymer clay, roll it out and carefully cut out a triangle. Then make holes of different sizes with cocktail tubes. WOW! It looks like a piece of cheese. Bake it. Now you have a cute earphone holder. We will also show you how to make awesome jewelries, such as watermelon or seashell necklaces, rainbow brooch, earrings with hearts. title: Kholifah Khilafatul Muslimin Bantah anti-Pancasila dan NKRI
description: KOMPAS.TV, LAMPUNG  Usai ramai video konvoi motor Khilafatul Muslimin di daerah Pulau Jawa, kholifah atau pimpinan pusat Khilafatul Muslimin membantah tudingan bahwa kelompoknya menentang Pancasila dan Negara Kesatuan Republik Indonesia (NKRI).||||Abdul Qodir Hasan Baraja menyebut, sejak berdirinya Khilafatul Muslimin pada tahun 1997, kegiatan seperti dalam video tersebut merupakan salah satu bagian dari syiar keagamaan.||||Baca Juga Bocah Korban Penusukan Jambret Butuh Bantuan Pengobatan di https://www.kompas.tv/article/294591/bocah-korban-penusukan-jambret-butuh-bantuan-pengobatan||||Kegiatan tersebut adalah agenda rutin yang dilakukan setiap bulannya, seperti di Jakarta, Berebes, dan Jawa Tengah.||||Selain itu, Abdul menegaskan bahwa Khilafatul Muslimin sangat mendukung Pancasila dan keutuhan NKRI. Bahkan, dalam kelompoknya juga terdapat warga non-Muslim yang juga ikut bergabung.||||"Maka Khilafatul Muslimin anggotanya Muslim dan non-Muslim. Jadi, gak cuma orang Muslim. Nah, ini yang gak dingerti sama orang seluruh dunia termasuk di negara karena terpengaruh pemikiran khilafah. Nah itu," jelasnya.||||Dalam penuturannya, kholifah Khilafatul Muslimin menerangkan bahwa Khilafatul Muslimin bertujuan mensyiarkan Islam sebagai rahmanan lil'alamin.||||Baca Juga Pelanggar Prokes Khilafatul Muslimin Dijerat Pasal Berlapis di https://www.kompas.tv/article/240217/pelanggar-prokes-khilafatul-muslimin-dijerat-pasal-berlapis||||Artinya, Khilafatul Muslimin berperan untuk menyatukan umat Muslim maupun non-Muslim dalam menjaga Pancasila dan kesatuan NKRI.||||#khilafatulmuslimin #pancasila #nkri||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/294919/kholifah-khilafatul-muslimin-bantah-anti-pancasila-dan-nkri

title: Daihatsu SIRION baru 2022
description: Setelah 4 tahun dijual di Indonesia, Daihatsu Sirion kini kembali mendapatkan versi facelift. Hanya saja, facelift kali ini nampak jauh lebih masif dibandingkan minor change yang dilakukan di tahun 2020 silam. Kini Daihatsu Sirion hadir dengan wajah yang lebih fresh dan kesan sporty yang lebih kental. Selain itu, Daihatsu Sirion 2022 juga telah dibekali sejumlah update fitur seperti Auto Headlamp, Ionizer dan juga Eco Idle alias Idling Start Stop.|Faktor krusial lain di Daihatsu Sirion 2022 ini adalah berubahnya transmisi otomatis dari 4 Speed Torque Converter menjadi CVT. Alhasil, mobil yang di Malaysia dikenal dengan nama Perodua Myvi ini menjadi mobil Daihatsu non DNGA pertama yang mencicipi transmisi D-CVT. Transmisi tersebut dipadukan dengan mesin 1NR-VE 1.300cc dan sistem gerak FWD yang membuatnya serupa dengan All New Daihatsu Xenia.|Seperti apa detailnya? title: Potret Kekompakan Prabowo dan Megawati Kala Hadiri Peresmian Smart Campus STIN
description: BOGOR, KOMPAS TV  Menteri Pertahanan RI Prabowo Subianto hadir bersama Megawati Soekarnoputri dalam peresmian Smart Campus Dr. (H.C) Ir. Soekarno Medical Intelligence Wangsa Avatara Sekolah Tinggi Intelijen Negara (STIN), Bogor.||||Keduanya menerima undangan dari Kepala BIN Jenderal Polisi (Purn.) Budi Gunawan.||||Tiba di kampus STIN, Prabowo disambut Kepala BIN dan disematkan pistol serta pisau khusus sebagai tanda penghormatan.||||Baca Juga Prabowo Subianto Akui Banyak Belajar dari Surya Paloh di https://www.kompas.tv/article/294879/prabowo-subianto-akui-banyak-belajar-dari-surya-paloh||||Kepala BIN menyebut bahwa Smart Campus ini merupakan terobosan teknologi dalam bidang pendidikan.||||Adapun Presiden kelima Megawati mendorong agar para taruna-taruni STIN dapat memiliki kepekaan dan data analisis yang kuat dalam menghadapi berbagai ancaman negara.||||Megawati dalam pidatonya di depan taruna dan taruni STIN juga sampaikan pentingnya pendidikan dan pengasahan batin.||||"Pendidikan itu sangat perlu, dan kami juga diasah yang namanya batin. title: Dari Partai Mana Anies Baswedan Akan Diusung? | Satu Meja The Forum (2)
description: KOMPASTV - Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan menjadi salah satu tokoh yang terus diperbincangkan lantaran disebut sebagai bakal calon presiden di Pilpres 2024. Terakhir, kehadiran Anies Baswedan di Milad Partai Keadilan Sejahtera (PKS) direspon dengan teriakan "presiden" oleh ribuan kader. ||||Nama Anies Baswedan juga kerap masuk dalam posisi 3 besar sejumlah hasil survei. Dengan elektabilitas ini, tidak heran jika ada parpol lain yang menginginkan Anies maju sebagai calon presiden mereka. Sebut saja Nasdem dan PPP. Nasdem secara resmi baru akan memutuskan siapa yang akan diusung dalam Rakernas pertengahan Juni, namun nama Anies Baswedan sudah banyak disuarakan.  PPP yang bergabung dengan Koalisi Indonesia Bersatu (KIB) juga belum memutuskan siapa yang diusung, namun suara-suara dukungan untuk Anies Baswedan terus disuarakan.||||Posisi Anies yang tidak bergabung dengan paprol membuatnya berstatus bebas transfer alias bisa diusung dan didukung oleh partai atau koalisi manapun.||||Lalu seberapa besar peluang Anies Baswedan? Siapa saja parpol yang akhirnya berhasil meminang? Saksikan talkshow Satu Meja The Forum "PELUANG CAPRES NONPARPOL" ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/294886/dari-partai-mana-anies-baswedan-akan-diusung-satu-meja-the-forum-2

title: On cam: Moment before KK collapsed in Kolkata hotel; Autopsy cites cardiac arrest as reason
description: CCTV footage shows Krishnakumar Kunnath walking in the lobby of a Kolkata hotel before falling sick. KK was taken to hospital after he reportedly collapsed in the hotel and was later declared brought dead. Questions have been raised about alleged lack of ventilation amid the extreme heat during the concert. The autopsy's initial report cited cardiac arrest as the cause of the singer's death. title: Presiden Jokowi Saksikan Konser Kebangsaan Bersama Masyarakat Ende, 1 Juni 2022
description: *Malam Terakhir di Ende, Presiden dan Ibu Iriana Saksikan Konser Kebangsaan Bersama Masyarakat*|Malam terakhir di Kabupaten Ende, pada Rabu, 1 Juni 2022, Presiden Joko Widodo beserta Ibu Iriana Joko Widodo menghabiskan malam bersama masyarakat dengan menonton pagelaran musik bertajuk konser kebangsaan, membumikan Pancasila dari NTT untuk Nusantara. |Konser kebangsaan yang digelar di Stadion Marilonga Ende tersebut mengundang sejumlah musisi Indonesia untuk menghibur masyarakat. Salah satu musisi Indonesia yang hadir yaitu Slank yang menyanyikan 17 lagu mereka. |Dengan mengenakan jaket berwarna merah berlogo G20, Presiden Jokowi hadir di stadion sekira pukul 21.25 WITA. Presiden beserta Ibu Iriana menyapa masyarakat yang hadir sembari berjalan memasuki Stadion Marilonga.|Presiden beserta Ibu Iriana tampak menikmati alunan musik Slank. Sesekali, Presiden menggerakkan kepala dan kakinya mengikuti irama lagu yang dimainkan. |Saat Slank menyanyikan lagu terakhir dalam konser tersebut, Presiden tampak beranjak dari kursi menuju panggung utama untuk menyampaikan apresiasi atas penampilan mereka.|Presiden juga menikmati penampilan dari Kla Project yang membawakan delapan lagunya. Ketika Katon Bagaskara menyanyikan lagu â€œTentang Kitaâ€, ia menuruni panggung dan bersalaman dengan Presiden dan Ibu Iriana, yang juga turut larut dalam alunan lagu Kla Project yang mendayu.|Setelah penampilan akhir dari Kla Project, Presiden Jokowi serta Ibu Iriana meninggalkan Stadion Marilonga.|Ende, 2 Juni 2022|Biro Pers, Media, dan Informasi Sekretariat Presiden|Website: https://www.presidenri.go.id|YouTube: Sekretariat Presiden

title: Portable Hydrogen Cartridge (Prototype)
description: Tokyo, Japan (June 2, 2022)â€•TOYOTA MOTOR CORPORATION ("Toyota") and its subsidiary, Woven Planet Holdings, Inc. ("Woven Planet"), have developed a working prototype of its portable hydrogen cartridge. This cartridge design will facilitate the everyday transport and supply of hydrogen energy to power a broad range of daily life applications in and outside of the home. Toyota and Woven Planet will conduct Proof of Concept ("PoC") trials in various places, including Woven City, a human-centered smart city of the future currently being constructed in Susono City, Shizuoka Prefecture.|More information: https://global.toyota/en/newsroom/corporate/37405994.html|Toyota Motor Corporation Official Global Website: https://global.toyota/en/|Toyota Motor Corporation on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/ToyotaMotorCorp/

title: Tulsa hospital shooting: At least 5 dead and multiple injured in Oklahoma, police say
description: Police have confirmed five people were killed in Tulsa, Okla., on Wednesday in a shooting at Saint Francisâ€™ Natalie Medical Building, including the gunman, from a self-inflicted gunshot wound.|Update: Police have identified the gunman who killed four at a hospital in Tulsa, Okla. on Wednesday as Michael Lewis, whose motive was found in a letter on his body, which "made it clear" that he intended to kill his doctor whom he blamed for the pain he experienced after back surgery on May 19.|According to a Tulsa police officer who was inside the building, the shooting happened on a lower floor and the victims appeared to be dressed as a doctor and nurses, though their official titles are not known at this time.  |Earlier Wednesday afternoon, police responded to a call about a man armed with a rifle in the building. title: At least 4 dead, multiple people injured in shooting at Tulsa, Oklahoma, medical building: Police
description: At least four people are dead and multiple people are injured following a shooting at the Natalie Building at St. Francis Hospital in Tulsa, Oklahoma, on Wednesday, according to police.|Police received a call of a man walking with a rifle near a medical office shortly before 5 p.m. local time. When police responded, they said it turned into an active shooter situation, according to Tulsa Police Captain Richard Meulenberg.|When police entered the building, they found multiple people shot in one area on the second floor, including in an orthopedic office, authorities said. The victims could be a combination both of employees and visitors, authorities initially said. The Natalie Building is a medical building on the hospital's campus.|"Officers immediately rushed to the second floor where the shooting was taking place, when they got there they found a few people had been shot, a couple were dead at that time," Meulenberg told ABC News. "We also found at that time who [we] believe and still believe to [be] the shooter because he had a long rifle and a pistol with him."|#tulsa #shooting #oklahoma |READ MORE: https://6abc.com/tulsa-oklahoma-active-shooter-shooting/11916398/

title: Keluarga Susul Ridwan Kamil ke Swiss Bantu Cari Eril Secara Mandiri di Sungai Aare
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS TV  Keluarga Ridwan Kamil terbang ke Swiss susul Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia bantu proses pencarian Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril.||||Hal tersebut disampaikan pihak keluarga saat memaparkan update perkembangan pencarian Eril di Sungai Aare, Swiss.||||Keluarga menyebut kini Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia sang istri turut membantu pencarian secara mandiri di bantaran sungai Aare.||||Baca Juga Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia Lakukan Pencarian Mandiri Eril Melalui Rute Darat sekitar Sungai Aare di https://www.kompas.tv/article/294774/ridwan-kamil-dan-atalia-lakukan-pencarian-mandiri-eril-melalui-rute-darat-sekitar-sungai-aare||||"Kang Emil dan Teh Lia sendiri juga melakukan proses pencarian secara mandiri, memang di tempat-tempat yang bisa mereka jangkau," ujar Erwin Muniruzaman, kakak Ridwan Kamil, Rabu (1/6).||||Perwakilan keluarga sudah terbang ke Swiss untuk membantu upaya tersebut.||||"Di sisi lain, perwakilan keluarga sudah terbang ke Swiss malam ini mereka akan mendarat di Swiss membantu Kang Emil dan Teh Lia," lanjutnya.||||Update pencarian Eril sudah disampaikan perwakilan keluarga, di mana hingga sepekan setelah dilaporkan hiilang, Eril belum ditemukan.||||Polisi di Bern Swiss disebut telah melakukan pencarian dengan berbagai metode.||||Video Editor: Firmansyah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/294909/keluarga-susul-ridwan-kamil-ke-swiss-bantu-cari-eril-secara-mandiri-di-sungai-aare

title: Ree Drummond's Herbed Lemon Pasta with Lobster and Steak Bites | The Pioneer Woman | Food Network
description: The Pioneer Woman's perfect date night dinner is a luxurious surf and turf pasta that features lemon-pepper beef tenderloin and buttery lobster!|Watch #ThePioneerWoman, Saturdays at 10a|9c + subscribe to #discoveryplus to stream the entire library and so much more: http://discoverypl.us/2NeKVgd. |Get the recipe â–¶ https://foodtv.com/383FGLl|Subscribe to Food Network â–¶ http://foodtv.com/YouTube|Take one sassy former city girl, her hunky rancher husband, a band of adorable kids, an extended family, cowboys, 3,000 wild mustangs, a herd of cattle and one placid basset hound and you have The Pioneer Woman. The Pioneer Woman is an open invitation into Ree Drummond's life: The award-winning blogger and best-selling cookbook author comes to Food Network and shares her special brand of home cooking, from throw-together suppers to elegant celebrations. The series, set against the incredible story of life at home on the range, is the next best thing to actually sitting on a stool in Ree's kitchen.|Welcome to Food Network, where learning to cook is as simple as clicking play! Grab your apron and get ready to get cookin' with some of the best chefs around the world. We'll give you a behind-the-scenes look at our best shows, take you inside our favorite restaurant and be your resource in the kitchen to make sure every meal is a 10/10!|Herbed Lemon Pasta with Lobster and Steak Bites|RECIPE COURTESY OF REE DRUMMOND|Level: Easy|Total: 45 min|Active: 40 min|Yield: 2 servings|Ingredients|8 ounces angel hair pasta|2 tablespoons olive oil|4 tablespoons salted butter|8 ounces cooked lobster knuckle and claw meat|Kosher salt and freshly ground black pepper|8 ounces beef tenderloin, cut into 1/2-inch cubes|1 tablespoon lemon pepper seasoning|1 shallot, diced small|2 cloves garlic, minced|1 tablespoon chopped fresh oregano|1 teaspoon fresh thyme leaves|Pinch red pepper flakes|1/4 cup white wine|1/4 cup heavy cream|1 lemon, zested and juiced|1/4 cup chopped fresh parsley|Directions|Cook the pasta until just al dente. Drain, reserving half a cup of pasta water. Set aside.|Add the olive oil and 2 tablespoons of the butter to a large, heavy-bottomed skillet over medium heat. When the butter has melted and the oil is hot, add the lobster meat and sprinkle with a pinch of salt and pepper, tossing until heated through, 5 to 10 minutes. Remove to a plate.|Sprinkle the steak with the lemon pepper seasoning and add to the skillet. Cook, turning occasionally, until medium-rare, 2 to 3 minutes. Remove to the plate. Without cleaning the skillet, melt the remaining 2 tablespoons butter, then add the shallots, garlic, oregano, thyme and red pepper flakes. Cook, stirring, until fragrant, about 30 seconds. Deglaze with the wine, scraping the skillet to release all the flavor. Add the cream, lemon zest and pasta water, then bring to a boil and let thicken, 1 to 2 minutes.|Add the pasta and toss to coat.|Transfer the pasta to a serving platter. Garnish with the parsley and drizzle over the lemon juice. Top with the lobster and steak bites.|Subscribe to our channel to fill up on the latest must-eat recipes, brilliant kitchen hacks and content from your favorite Food Network shows.|â–¶ FOOD NETWORK KITCHEN APP: http://foodtv.com/FNKApp|â–¶ WEBSITE: https://www.foodnetwork.com|â–¶ FULL EPISODES: https://watch.foodnetwork.com|â–¶ FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/FoodNetwork|â–¶ INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/FoodNetwork|â–¶ TWITTER: https://twitter.com/FoodNetwork|#ReeDrummond #ThePioneerWoman #FoodNetwork #HerbedLemonPasta #LobsterAndSteakBites|Ree Drummond's Herbed Lemon Pasta with Lobster and Steak Bites | The Pioneer Woman | Food Network|https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JgeAAzocq2s

title: Johnny Depp Trial VERDICT Announced
description: Johnny Depp won his defamation trial against ex-wife Amber Heard. Depp sued Heard in response to an op-ed she wrote about being the victim of domestic abuse, which the actor claimed negatively impacted his career. title: Denmark wants to join EU defense policy - Why is this significant? | DW News
description: It appears voters in Denmark have said yes to the country joining the European Union's common defense policy. |According to a public broadcaster exit poll, more than 69 percent have supported the plan in a referendum. |Denmark is an EU member but in the past negotiated an exemption on the bloc's defense policy. Now, against a backdrop of Russian aggression, Danes were asked whether they want to opt in. |Also, Sweden and Finland are pushing ahead with their landmark bids to join NATO. For Sweden, joining the military alliance would mean giving up more than two centuries of neutrality. Public opinion in favour of joining grew to around 50 percent after Russia invaded Ukraine. |But NATO-member Turkey opposes the bids. Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan accuses Sweden of supporting terrorists and is angry about Stockholm's embargo on arms sales to Turkey. |Speaking exclusively to DW News, Swedish Defense Minister, Peter Hultqvist explained what was behind his country's historic shift. |Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#NATO #Denmark #NordicShift

title: OBI-WAN KENOBI Ep3: Every Star Wars EASTER EGG and Full BREAKDOWN
description: Thanks to Keeps for sponsoring this video! Go to â€‹https://www.keeps.com/screencrush â€‹to get 50% off your first order of Keeps hair loss treatment.|Obi-Wan Kenobi's third episodes features the former Jedi Master finally crossing sabers with his old apprentice, Darth Vader. There are also numerous other connections to the Star wars universe, including the Clone Wars, Luke Skywalker, Revenge of the Sith, and many more.|If you're new, Subscribe! â†’ http://bit.ly/subscribe-screencrush|Go here â†’ http://screencrush.com/|Like us â†’ https://www.facebook.com/ScreenCrush|Follow us â†’ https://twitter.com/screencrushnews|Get our newsletter â†’ http://screencrush.com/newsletter/|Written and Hosted by Ryan Arey (http://twitter.com/ryanarey)|Research by SrinidhinRao|Edited by Randolf Nombrado, Srinidhi Rao, and Ian Dugan|The episode opens with Obi wan still praying to Qui Gon, waiting for his master to speak to him. You remember that up until this point, itâ€™s not normal for a jedi to survive after death and to speak to the living. Qui Gon is able to do this because he had a strong connection to the living forceâ€“the part of the force thatâ€™s generated by all living things.|In Revenge of the Sith, through mediation, Yoda was able to hear Qui Gon's voice. Which is why he tells Obi that heâ€™ll teach him how to speak to him.|But, Obi wan hasnâ€™t quite mastered the technique yet, probably because he is not at peace with himself, and is not balanced. Remember, Rey had a similar problem in Rise of Skywalker. Sorry, wrong clip, I mean this clip.|Instead of hearing Qui Gon, Obi wan can only hear the voice of Reva revealing Anakin is alive, and the voices from his past. This quote is Yoda, when he warned Obi to not look at the records of order 66 in Revenge of the Sith. And then he hears Qui Gon's dying words. And finally his final confrontation with Anakin. |Then we cut to Vader in Bacta, like we first saw in Rogue One, being reassembled. Notice his suit is a bit different from what you may be used to. This actually matched what he wore in A New Hope. The forehead of the helmet is a bit bigger, the eyes are smaller, and they have red lenses. There was a nod to these red lenses in Revenge of the Sith, when he first wears the helmet.|This is Vaderâ€™s palace on Mustafar. This is, of course, where Obi Wan and Anakin dueled and Vader was very badly burned. |But Mustafar is also the location of a strong dark side nexus, so Vader ordered his palace to be designed there. He commissioned a Sith architect to build this structure as a way to harness dark side energy, which he then used to enter the realm of the dead, and speak to Padme. But once he saw her, she didnâ€™t recognize him because he was overcome with the dark side.|We later saw more of the palace in Rogue one, but now we get to see his throne room, and James Earl Jones returns to voice Vader.|Back on the ship, Obi Wan says. Now what he means by that is that there are hyperspace lanes all throughout the galaxy. These are safe paths through subspace where you wonâ€™t accidentally materialize into a sun or something. Which is why trade routes were able to be taxed in the opening crawl of The Phantom Menace.|When Leia asked Ben to use the force he says, which Iâ€™m sure made us all think of this. No, I mean this.|His explanation of the force was very touching though. And I thought it was sweet that he explained the force to Leia for the first time, just like he did for Luke. Obi wan fixes the droid Lola. Many of you pointed out that the droid looks like the saucer aliens in the movie batteries not includedâ€“and those aliens were created by industrial light and magic, George Lucas's VFX company.|Addled Apostate on twitter mentions that the way Leia's braid falls makes her look like the padawan she would never get to properly be.|When they sneak off the ship we can see the imperial crest on the crates. This is very similar to the republic crest, except the palatine had two pillars taken awayâ€“one of them represented the Jedi, and the other one was symbolic of your mom.|When they land there is an R5 astromech model droid right here.|And boy, Obi wan is always smuggling himself onto and off of  something isnâ€™t he? |Then we got to the inquisitor ship landing at Fortress Inquisitorius on Nur. This headquarters of the inquisitors previously appeared in Jedi: Fallen Order and the Darth Vader comics. Notice how the shuttle, the fortress, and Vader's palace all have twin towers at the top. This is to represent the sith rule of 2, that there can only ever be one master and one apprentice. Any more than that and the sith start killing each other. The sith power structure works like a pyramid with palpatine on top, and the inquisitors at the bottom. This is why the shape of a Sith holocron is a pyramid. |#ObiWanKenobi #EasterEggs #StarWars

title: Herschel Walkerâ€™s answer on gun violence is literally nonsensical. Itâ€™s not the first time.
description: Herschel Walker has a pattern of offering questionable answers, avoiding the media and has been accused of making threats against women. In todayâ€™s episode of The Point, CNNâ€™s Chris Cillizza breaks down how despite all that, heâ€™s the GOP candidate for Senate in Georgia, capturing former President Donald Trumpâ€™s endorsement along the way.|==|Herschel Walker's answer on gun violence is literally nonsensical|Analysis by Chris Cillizza, CNN Editor-at-large|Less than 48 hours after a gunman killed 19 children and two teachers at an elementary school in Uvalde, Texas, Georgia Republican Senate nominee Herschel Walker was asked on Fox about the nation's gun violence problem -- and what to do about it.|Here's what he said Thursday morning:|"Cain killed Abel and that's a problem that we have. What we need to do is look into how we can stop those things. You know, you talked about doing a disinformation -- what about getting a department that can look at young men that's looking at women that's looking at their social media. What about doing that? Looking into things like that and we can stop that that way. But yet they want to just continue to talk about taking away your constitutional rights. And I think there's more things we need to look into. This has been happening for years and the way we stop it is putting money into the mental health field, by putting money into other departments rather than departments that want to take away your rights."|Read more at: https://www.cnn.com/2022/05/26/politics/herschel-walker-gun-violence-fox-news/index.html

title: Doctor Reacts To DRAMATIC Lifeguard Rescues
description: Bondi Rescue is an Australian reality show about the lifeguards who work at Bondi Beach in Sydney. They have a YouTube channel where they upload a ton of their most amazing clips, so I decided to take a look and evaluate their skills from a medical perspective. Today we talk about drowning, CPR, chest compressions, the difference between CPR on land and in the sea, dislocated fingers, dislocated hips, seizures, diabetes, blue bottles or jellyfish stings, scrapes, and all other injuries that can occur when surfing or swimming in the ocean. Are there any clips I missed? Let me know down below!|I LOVE reading your comments and take your suggestions seriously. title: Camila Cabello - Lola (Official Live Performance) | Vevo ft. Yotuel
description: Camila Cabello - Lola | Vevo Official Live Performance|Camila Cabello says that making her third album â€˜Familia' was â€œfun, joyful, and easy.â€ That sentiment extends to our Official Live Performance collaboration, which was staged at a Simi Valley, California ranch where blockbuster films are shot. Cabello commanded the camera like an A-list actor while performing four songs from the new record. The album's tender artwork, with Camila embracing a young cousin, parallels its heartfelt title, and she's made it clear that this music was meant to explore her family's roots. Both Latin rhythms and Spanish-language vocals - imbued throughout the album - help in that goal. To that effect, â€œLolaâ€ is perhaps her most overt effort, not only because it taps Yotuel Romero for a duet, but because of its content.  The Cuban singer of Orishas fame was kind enough to join us on set, where they did total justice to a heartfelt track that touches on immigrant dreams and promises unfulfilled. A fitting closer for our stunning collaboration that documents a Camila Cabello finding her most authentic self. |Watch Camila Cabello videos: title: Kevin Durant shuts down Draymond Green's take on Steph Curry's legacy | NBA | FIRST THINGS FIRST
description: Draymond Green shared some thoughts with Colin Cowherd on the narrative that Stephen Curry needed a Finals MVP award to validate his legacy. Green pointed out that even while Kevin Durant was on the roster, Steph was facing double teams more often than KD was, and a Finals MVP isn't going to change the impact he's had on the game. KD took to social media to say Draymond's take was 100% false, and the two had a brief back and forth on this topic. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. title: Russian pilot's showoff ends in close shave; 'Alligator' nearly swept its tail into water
description: The pilot of a Russian Ka-52 combat reconnaissance & attack chopper intended to put up a show for onlookers. The idea nearly ended in a disaster, the incident ended up being a close shave for both civilians & the chopper crew. 2 Ka-52s were flying at a low altitude above a reservoir in Alchevsk city (so-called Luhansk People's Republic). The Russian pilot saw people on the ground recording & decided to show off the chopper's features. Lead chopper maneuvered out of position; pilot wanted to show the famed sideways flying abilities of the Ka-52. When approaching the shore, the Ka-52 shook vigorously - at one point, the tail nearly swept into the water.
